```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    title Document Status State Machine - Assinafy Integration

    [*] --> uploading: Upload initiated

    uploading --> uploaded: File received
    uploaded --> metadata_processing: Processing started

    metadata_processing --> metadata_ready: Processing complete
    metadata_processing --> failed: Processing error

    metadata_ready --> pending_signature: Assignment created

    pending_signature --> certificating: All signatures collected
    pending_signature --> rejected_by_signer: Signer rejects
    pending_signature --> rejected_by_user: User cancels
    pending_signature --> expired: Deadline reached

    certificating --> certificated: Certification complete
    certificating --> failed: Certification error

    rejected_by_signer --> [*]: Process terminated
    rejected_by_user --> [*]: Process terminated
    certificated --> [*]: Process complete
    failed --> [*]: Process terminated

    expired --> [*]: Process terminated

    note right of uploading
        Initial state after
        POST /documents
    end note

    note right of metadata_ready
        Document ready for
        assignment creation
    end note

    note right of pending_signature
        Waiting for signers
        to complete
    end note

    note right of certificated
        Final state - artifact
        ready for download
    end note

    note right of expired
        Automatic transition
        after expires_at
    end note
```
